The paper deals with the problem of spoofing attacks, which is a common issue in computer security (cs.CR). The proposed algorithm involves the use of geometrical and tropical analysis, which are techniques commonly used in information theory (cs.IT) and signal processing (cs.SI). The algorithm also involves the use of image processing techniques, which are commonly used in computer vision (cs.CV). Finally, the algorithm involves the use of machine learning techniques, which are commonly used in machine learning (cs.LG).
